        At Royal Paradise, our focus is on creating sanctuaries that refresh, refuel and renew 
        with an accent on health and wellness. The benefits of yoga have been known for 
        centuries now and they are only more relevant in today&#39;s times. This is probably 
        the first time in the world that a hotel chain has offered in room yoga. 
